video_description: Cool new commercial where a rider on a 2012 FXDWG Wide Glide hooks up a bunch of leashes to dog cages and rides off. Liberating the pooches. Video ends with a cool scruffy dog on the back of the bike wearing  doggles! Love this new direction with "No Cages" theme.
title: Liberation - New Funny Harley-Davidson Commercial
